---
title: Sweet Chili Beef & Cabbage Stir-Fry with Rice, Cashews & Crispy Fried Onions
description: Forget takeout: The path to sweet-and-savory dinner bliss is only 15 quick minutes away! In this recipe, ground beef, shredded carrots, and cabbage are coated in a sumptuous sweet chili–soy sauce glaze. Everything comes together over a bed of fluffy quick-cooking rice with a crunchy garnish of cashews and crispy fried onions.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67325e10ba08659748634757-19314614.jpeg
